general.gigTitle: setup customize develop website by mylisting theme and listingpro

sellerCard.oneLiner: Professional Web Designer, WordPress and Web Developer
sellerCard.description:
Hi,
I offer complete, all-inclusive WordPress website design and development. From a simple brochure website to an advanced e-Commerce solution with an integrated forum or membership website, I can create the ultimate solution to meet your marketing. I have highly experience in WordPress, HTML5, CSS3, Bootstrap, jQuery & PHP.

description.content:
Hi,

In this Gig, I will Provide a custom directory WordPress website using Mylisting theme or Listingpro theme, making sure that it's built in the most appropriate way to serve your needs and to give you the possibility to be able to edit all the content on your own for future purposes.


What I will offer :


  • Branding & Design
  • Mylisting or Listing Pro Theme Installation
  • Customize according to your requirements
  • Complete Theme Demo or Layout import
  • Install security system for website protection
  • Claim & Verify Listing
  • Invoice System
  • Integrations Listing
  • Promote Listing Product
  • Setup Categories, Tags & Regions
  • Setup Payment Packages
  • Develop Explore Page as per your Requirements
  • User Sign In/Register functionality
  • Fully integrated with WP Job Manager
  • Powerful search facet editor, unique to each listing type
  • And also Develop Admin, Vendors & Clients Dashboard
  • Setup Appointment booking system
  • Will help you import or upload Listing



Some Extra Feature:


  • Multiple Restaurant Bookings For Listing Profiles. Extra - 90$
  • Multiple Language. Extra - 80$
  • Multiple Salon Bookings Services For Listing Profiles. Extra - 100$



If you have any question. Please contact before placing any order.


Thanks

Very professional, quality job and very fast, we will continue to work with him! Thank you Tamim

Tamim is always quick to respond and is extremely helpful in solving any issues or concerns. He's always willing to customize requests for his clients and is highly skilled in WordPress. I highly recommend him and will not hesitate to work with him again for my future startup projects or development.

My website is BETTER because of Tamin. His work ethic was a pleasure to experience. He transformed my OLD LISTING PRO website to the MY LISTING theme, because I was so annoyed with the outdated LISTING PRO template and their lack of knowledge. He took time and patience to make sure every detail and more was completed!
